1 at the lowest net system cost to ratepayers over the expected
2 useful life of the resource. The commission's determination of cost
3 is subject to all of the following:
4 (A) The commission shall deduct the projected value of any
5 federal tax incentives, carbon reduction credits, or production
6 credits that directly reduce the revenue requirement charged to
7 ratepayers. This sub-subparagraph applies only to a resource that
8 constitutes a dispatchable resource capable of providing firm
