23 finds that completion of the project or program is no longer
24 reasonable and prudent, the commission may modify or cancel
25 approval of the project or program and unincurred costs in the
26 electric utility's integrated resource plan. Except for costs the
27 commission finds an electric utility has incurred as the result of
28 fraud, concealment, gross mismanagement, or lack of quality
29 controls amounting to gross mismanagement, if commission approval
